  "summary": "Use this dossier when a Next.js App Router project needs Clerk authentication wired at the app shell level. It provides the essential integration pattern: `ClerkProvider` in the root layout, Clerk middleware for request handling, and guidance for protecting routes and rendering auth UI.",
